dct_title_s: South Shetland Islands : scale 1:200 000 / compiled by M. Biszczuk, Mapping and Geographic Information Centre, British Antarctic Survey, 2008. (Verso)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, isolines, shading, and spot heights. Depths shown by contours and gradient tints. Panel title. At head of panel title: British Antarctic Survey. Includes notes, statistical data, index of historic sites (HSMs), index of protected areas (ASPAs), sheet coverage map, magnetic declination diagrams, and col. ill.
dct_publisher_sm: Cambridge, UK : British Antarctic Survey, c2008.
